01:22:54,795 --> 01:22:56,547
Mereka menuju breezeway
di sisi utara.

1085
01:22:56,588 --> 01:22:57,505
Aku akan ke sana.

1086
01:23:07,055 --> 01:23:09,057
Hei, Gates!

1087
01:23:14,895 --> 01:23:18,274
Sudah cukup!
Berikan dokumennya kepadaku.

1088
01:23:19,399 --> 01:23:21,609
Baiklah, Phil.

1089
01:23:38,416 --> 01:23:41,418
Awas! Minggir!

1090
01:23:44,921 --> 01:23:46,757
Awas!

1091
01:24:28,876 --> 01:24:31,086
Biarkan! Lepaskan mereka.

